name: Holistic Neurosynaptic Template
description: Neurosynaptic profiles are invaluable to the Triglavians for assessing any sentients they encounter but acquiring a Holistic Neurosynaptic Template for a given personality is real prize. An inclusive data set such as this records every nuance of personality laid down in core and peripheral neurosynaptic pathway. The Collective will trade premium items for such high quality data.
